yapwaf
======

A small WSGI application framework for a software engineering class project.


Installation
------------
Simply run 'python setup.py develop' in order to get this working in a development
fashion.  Switch 'develop' for 'intstall' in order for non-development installation.

Running
-------
The 'yapwaf' script that will be in your path after installation provides all the
necessary tools to create, maintain, and run a YAPWAF application.

Testing
-------
There are tests in the testing directory.  Simply execute 'testify tests.tests'
to run them.

Examples
--------
There is an examples directory that contains one example application that shows
off many of the tools that YAPWAF provides.
